ouse Lottery”。 “Nijisanji HEROES Seaside House”颁奖典礼将在游乐设施“Namco”和Namco Online Crane举行。</p><p>点击<a href="https://estream-store.com/lp/umi-project/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>查看特别合作网站。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000001439.000006792.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cyber​​Z Co., Ltd.新闻稿</a></p><h2>举办“贝尔佑五郎和水梨凛能做的V的广播”公开录音活动</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/0c80e286f5ae60429af295bc2e3b0562-kix.8ggwd5n9koe1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/0c80e286f5ae60429af295bc2e3b0562-kix.8ggwd5n9koe1-1024x538.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/0c80e286f5ae60429af295bc2e3b0562-kix.8ggwd5n9koe1-1024x538.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/0c80e286f5ae60429af295bc2e3b0562-kix.8ggwd5n9koe1-300x158.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/0c80e286f5ae60429af295bc2e3b0562-kix.8ggwd5n9koe1-768x403.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/0c80e286f5ae60429af295bc2e3b0562-kix.8ggwd5n9koe1-1536x806.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/0c80e286f5ae60429af295bc2e3b0562-kix.8ggwd5n9koe1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="538" /></a></p><p>广播节目“<a href="https://hibiki-radio.jp/description/holostars-yaruv/detail" target="_blank" rel="noopener">[Holostars 5th Anniversary]V的广播，Yugoro Bell和Rinou Mizunashi可以做”的</a>公开录音活动<a href="https://holostars-yaruv-kouroku.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">将于9月14日星期六在船堀大厅举行</a>。</p><p>本次活动是<a href="https://twitter.com/holostarstv" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Holostars</a>节目的首次广播活动，两位广播主持人<a href="https://x.com/yukokuroberu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yugoro Robel</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/minaserioch" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rinno Mizunashi</a>将在活动会场展示公开录音中独有的计划、角落和演讲。</p><p> <a href="https://eplus.jp/sf/detail/4140500001-P0030001?P6=001&amp;P1=0402